-teachers-work-free-time-2025-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20substitute%20for%20a%20doctor%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2026%2C%20Kevin%20Choi%20got%20a%20diagnosis%20that%20changed%20his%20life%3A%20glaucoma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20progressive%20eye%20disease%20that%20damages%20the%20optic%20nerve%2C%20often%20without%20symptoms%20until%20it's%20too%20late.%20By%20the%20time%20doctors%20caught%20it%2C%20Choi%20had%20lost%20half%20his%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20engineer%20by%20training%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20former%20rifleman%20in%20South%20Korea's%20Marine%20Corps%20%E2%80%94%20Choi%20thought%20he%20had%20a%20solid%20handle%20on%20his%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20really%20frustrated%20I%20didn't%20notice%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202016%20diagnosis%20still%20gives%20him%20%26quot%3Bpanic.%26quot%3B%20But%20it%20also%20sparked%20something%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20Choi%20teamed%20up%20with%20his%20doctor%2C%20a%20vitreoretinal%20surgeon%2C%20to%20cofound%20Mediwhale%2C%20a%20South%20Korea-based%20healthtech%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20mission%20is%20to%20use%20AI%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecatch%20diseases%20before%20symptoms%20show%20up%20and%20cause%20irreversible%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20the%20person%20who%20feels%20the%20value%20of%20that%20the%20most%2C%26quot%3B%20Choi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20can%20screen%20for%20cardiovascular%2C%20kidney%2C%20and%20eye%20diseases%20through%20non-invasive%20retinal%20scans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMediwhale's%20technology%20is%20primarily%20used%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20and%20hospitals%20in%20Dubai%2C%20Italy%2C%20and%20Malaysia%20have%20also%20adopted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMediwhale%20said%20in%20September%20that%20it%20had%20raised%20%2412%20million%20in%20its%20Series%20A2%20funding%20round%2C%20led%20by%20Korea%20Development%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b835d544-2dbd-4649-b01a-6d7e87c10921%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Choi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68640897f748d8c055f4ba12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAntoine%20Mutin%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b835d544-2dbd-4649-b01a-6d7e87c10921%5C%22%3EAI%20can%20help%20with%20fast%2C%20early%20screening%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChoi%20believes%20AI%20is%20most%20powerful%20in%20the%20earliest%20stage%20of%20care%3A%20screening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20can%20help%20healthcare%20providers%20make%20faster%2C%20smarter%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20that%20can%20mean%20the%20difference%20between%20early%20intervention%20and%20irreversible%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20conditions%2C%20%26quot%3Bspeed%20is%20the%20most%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Choi%20said.%20That's%20true%20for%20%26quot%3Bsilent%20killers%26quot%3B%20like%20heart%20and%20kidney%20disease%2C%20and%20progressive%20conditions%20like%20glaucoma%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20often%20show%20no%20early%20symptoms%20but%2C%20unchecked%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20permanent%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20patients%20with%20chronic%20conditions%20like%20diabetes%20or%20obesity%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20even%20higher.%20Early%20complications%20can%20lead%20to%20dementia%2C%20liver%20disease%2C%20heart%20problems%2C%20or%20kidney%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20these%20risks%20are%20spotted%2C%20the%20more%20options%20doctors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20patients%20%E2%80%94%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoi%20said%20Mediwhale's%20AI%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20triage%20by%20flagging%20who's%20low-risk%2C%20who%20needs%20monitoring%2C%20and%20who%20should%20see%20a%20doctor%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScreening%20patients%20at%20the%20first%20point%20of%20contact%20doesn't%20require%20%26quot%3Bvery%20deep%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20Choi%20said.%20That%20kind%20of%20quick%2C%20low-friction%20risk%20assessment%20is%20where%20AI%20shines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMediwhale's%20tool%20lets%20patients%20bypass%20traditional%20procedures%20%E2%80%94%20including%20blood%20tests%2C%20CT%20scans%2C%20and%20ultrasounds%20%E2%80%94%20when%20screening%20for%20cardiovascular%20and%20kidney%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoi%20also%20said%20that%20when%20patients%20see%20their%20risks%20visualized%20through%20retinal%20scans%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20take%20it%20more%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a6e82c9-5653-43cb-9854-889678e78257%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226014%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Choi%20on%20the%20street%20in%20Seoul%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685551c9f748d8c055f40a22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224009%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChoi%20said%20AI%20can%20help%20healthcare%20providers%20make%20faster%2C%20smarter%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20that%20can%20mean%20the%20difference%20between%20early%20intervention%20and%20irreversible%20harm.%3Cp%3EAntoine%20Mutin%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a6e82c9-5653-43cb-9854-889678e78257%5C%22%3EAI%20won't%20replace%20doctors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20belief%20in%20AI's%20power%2C%20Choi%20is%20clear%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-ai-job-shortages-doctors-teachers-work-free-time-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20a%20replacement%20for%20doctors.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatients%20want%20to%20hear%20a%20human%20doctor's%20opinion%20and%20reassurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoi%20also%20said%20that%20medicine%20is%20often%20messier%20than%20a%20clean%20dataset.%20While%20AI%20is%20%26quot%3Bbrilliant%20at%20solving%20defined%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20lacks%20the%20ability%20to%20navigate%20nuance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMedicine%20often%20requires%20a%20different%20dimension%20of%20decision-making%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%3A%20How%20will%20a%20specific%20treatment%20affect%20someone's%20life%3F%20Will%20they%20follow%20through%3F%20How%20is%20their%20emotional%20state%20affecting%20their%20condition%3F%20These%20are%20all%20variables%20that%20algorithms%20still%20struggle%20to%20read%2C%20but%20doctors%20can%20pick%20up.%20These%20insights%20%26quot%3Bgo%20beyond%20simple%20data%20points%2C%26quot%3B%20Choi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20patients%20push%20back%20%E2%80%94%20say%2C%20hesitating%20to%20start%20a%20new%20medication%20%E2%80%94%20doctors%20are%20trained%20to%20both%20understand%20why%20and%20guide%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bnavigate%20patients'%20irrational%20behaviours%20while%20still%20grounding%20decisions%20in%20quantitative%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20complex%20decision-making%20processes%20that%20extend%20far%20beyond%20simply%20processing%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-choi-mediwhale-ai-doctor-vision-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751846402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68555208f748d8c055f40a29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-choi-mediwhale-ai-doctor-vision-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kevin%20Choi%20uses%20AI%20to%20detect%20critical%20diseases%20early%20through%20retinal%20scans.%20He%20said%20AI%20helps%20in%20screening%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20replace%20doctors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmlee%40insider.com%20(Lee%20Chong%20Ming)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-choi-mediwhale-ai-doctor-vision-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22