Fvisiting-dublin-tips-from-local-born-in-ireland%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisiting%20Dublin%20for%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Irish%20city%20was%20cleaner%2C%20kinder%2C%20and%20more%20vegetarian-friendly%20than%20I%20imagined%20it%20would%20be.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20surprised%20how%20lax%20local%20tipping%20culture%20differed%20from%20what%20I%20was%20used%20to%20in%20the%20US.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20felt%20a%20connection%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-traveling-to-dublin-ireland%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDublin%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20about%20my%20entire%20life%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20not%20because%20of%20ancestral%20history.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20last%20name%20(Dubin)%20is%20just%20one%20letter%20away%2C%20and%20most%20of%20my%20mail%20comes%20misspelled%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20city%20instead.%20True%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%20similarity%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20I've%20flown%20all%20around%20the%20world%20in%20my%20role%20as%20a%20travel%20writer%2C%20I'd%20never%20actually%20been%20to%20the%20Irish%20capital%20city%20until%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20visit%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20and%20felt%20inspired%20to%20visit%20again.%20Here's%20what%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20discover%20during%20my%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-to-dublin-ireland%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Dublin%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELocals%20I%20encountered%20seemed%20incredibly%20warm%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20in%20a%20performative%20way.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flowers%20on%20display%20outside%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed21185e81483682cf0a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20encountered%20many%20kind%20locals%20throughout%20my%20trip.%20%3Cp%3EAlesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20heard%20many%20people%20rave%20about%20Irish%20hospitality%2C%20and%20Dublin%20didn't%20disappoint%20on%20that%20front.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20really%20stood%20out%20to%20me%20was%20how%20genuine%20the%20friendliness%20from%20locals%20felt.%20It%20wasn't%20the%20kind%20of%20overly%20rehearsed%2C%20customer-service-polished%20vibe%20you%20sometimes%20find%20in%20touristy%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20I%20encountered%20felt%20kind%2C%20helpful%2C%20and%20funny%20in%20a%20natural%2C%20unforced%20way.%20Our%20driver%20cracked%20jokes%20and%20gave%20us%20tons%20of%20travel%20tips%20that%20had%20rich%20local%20flavor%2C%20but%20didn't%20feel%20like%20a%20shtick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20city%20gave%20off%20a%20low-key%2C%20welcoming%20energy%20that%20stayed%20with%20me%20long%20after%20I%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMore%20restaurants%20had%20vegetarian%20options%20than%20I%20expected.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interior%20of%20a%20pub%20with%20flags%20hung%20from%20ceiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed1b5f748d8c055f489a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20online%20menus%20didn't%20seem%20vegetarian-friendly%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20options%20once%20I%20asked%20in%20real%20life.%3Cp%3EAlesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20vegetarian%2C%20I%20came%20in%20with%20pretty%20low%20expectations%20for%20the%20variety%20of%20foods%20I'd%20get%20to%20eat%20when%20it%20came%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-go-in-ireland-not-dublin-tips-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edining%20out%20in%20Dublin%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Local%20cuisine%20tends%20to%20rely%20heavily%20on%20meat%2C%20from%20Irish%20breakfasts%20to%20pies%20and%20stews.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20menus%20I%20browsed%20had%20lots%20of%20meat%20dishes%20and%20it%20initially%20looked%20like%20plant-based%20options%20would%20be%20few%20and%20far%20between.%20However%2C%20once%20I%20asked%20restaurant%20staff%20in%20person%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20accommodating%20most%20places%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20servers%20brought%20out%20full%20vegetarian%20menus%20that%20weren't%20printed%20and%20only%20available%20to%20customers%20who%20requested%20them.%20Others%20happily%20offered%20to%20have%20something%20special%20prepared%20from%20the%20kitchen%20or%20make%20vegetarian-friendly%20menu%20swaps.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELocal%20tipping%20culture%20felt%20more%20low-key%20than%20what%20I%20was%20used%20to%20back%20home.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Alesandra%20Dubin%20sipping%20a%20Guiness%20in%20a%20bar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed278f748d8c055f489c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20bit%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20local%20tipping%20culture%20in%20Dublin.%3Cp%3EAlesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20tipping%20feels%20mandatory.%20In%20Dublin%2C%20it%20just%20didn't%20seem%20like%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20Americans%2C%20I'm%20conditioned%20to%20tip%20generously%20(sometimes%20even%20going%20way%20above%20what's%20suggested)%20in%20restaurants%20or%20service%20settings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20tossing%20down%20a%20few%20extra%20euros%2C%20tipping%20didn't%20seem%20to%20be%20expected%20at%20casual%20caf%C3%A9s%20or%20bars.%20Even%20at%20sit-down%20restaurants%2C%20tipping%20our%20server%2010%25%20seemed%20ample%2C%20whereas%2020%25%20feels%20like%20the%20typical%20minimum%20back%20at%20home%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20lax%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftipping-culture-customers-cut-back-survey-says-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etipping%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20definitely%20took%20some%20getting%20used%20to%2C%20but%20once%20I%20adjusted%2C%20it%20felt%20refreshingly%20pressure%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20clean%20the%20city%20felt.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Alesandra%20Dubin%20smiling%20on%20busy%20street%20in%20Dubling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed1643d5881a51c1c4198%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20couldn't%20believe%20how%20quickly%20Dublin%20cleaned%20up%20after%20its%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20parade.%20%3Cp%3EAlesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDublin's%20streets%20were%20some%20of%20the%20cleanest%20I've%20seen%20in%20a%20major%20European%20city.%20This%20was%20an%20especially%20impressive%20feat%2C%20given%20that%20I%20visited%20the%20city%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fst-patricks-day-celebrated-differences-ireland-us-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESt.%20Patrick's%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20had%20hosted%20a%20massive%20parade%20and%20beers%20and%20crowds%20spilled%20out%20of%20every%20pub%20the%20cleanup%20was%20surprisingly%20swift%20and%20civilized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20expecting%20a%20bit%20more%20grit%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20high-traffic%20areas%20around%20the%20city%20center%20or%20Temple%20Bar%20%E2%80%94%20but%20even%20those%20looked%20remarkably%20tidy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESidewalks%20were%20free%20of%20litter%2C%20public%20trash%20bins%20weren't%20overflowing%2C%20and%20I%20never%20once%20encountered%20the%20kind%20of%20mess%20that%20can%20be%20common%20outside%20of%20crowded%2C%20late-night%20spots.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20city%20with%20so%20much%20foot%20traffic%20(and%20so%20many%20pubs)%2C%20it%20was%20honestly%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20city%20feels%20cozy%20and%20cosmopolitan%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Alesandra%20Dubin%20sitting%20at%20a%20picnic%20table%20outside%20of%20a%20building%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed24c85e81483682cf0b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20fun%20to%20step%20away%20to%20spots%20like%20Avoca%20Mill.%20%3Cp%3EAlesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDublin%20hits%20that%20rare%20sweet%20spot%3A%20it's%20a%20capital%20city%20with%20real%20cultural%20and%20historical%20heft%2C%20but%20it%20still%20feels%20approachable%20and%20easy%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20greater%20area%20population%20around%20a%20million%20(and%20a%20Dublin%20city%20population%20substantially%20smaller)%2C%20I%20never%20felt%20overwhelmed%20by%20crowds%20or%20traffic.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20many%20major%20sights%20were%20walkable.%20Even%20when%20the%20city%20center%20was%20packed%20for%20the%20holiday%20events%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20navigate%20in%20and%20around%20the%20area.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20no%20trouble%20making%20my%20way%20to%20several%20sights%20outside%20the%20urban%20area%2C%20from%20Avoca%20Mill%20(the%20country's%20oldest%20working%20hand-weaving%20mill)%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-colors-analyzed-by-pro-told-me-what-to-wear-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKildare%20Village%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20luxury%20shopping%20outpost).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20strong%20creative%20energy%20in%20the%20air%20%E2%80%94%20from%20bookstores%20and%20galleries%20to%20street%20musicians%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20overall%20pace%20is%20slower%20and%20more%20relaxed%20than%20what%20I've%20experienced%20in%20bigger%20European%20capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-going-to-dublin-first-time-from-american-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751805841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed3b085e81483682cf100%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-going-to-dublin-first-time-from-american-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20an%20American%2C%20my%20first%20trip%20to%20Dublin%20was%20filled%20with%20surprises%20about%20locals%2C%20tipping%20culture%2C%20vegetarian%20options%2C%20and%20more%20parts%20of%20the%20Irish%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehochberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Alesandra%20Dubin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-going-to-dublin-first-time-from-american-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Richard%20Greenberg%2C%20Tony-Winning%20%E2%80%98Take%20Me%20Out%E2%80%99%20Playwright%2C%20Dies%20at%2067%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751805254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F05%2Fgreenberglight.jpg%3Fw%3D800%26h%3D533%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236448059%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Richard%20Greenberg%2C%20the%20Tony%20Award-winning%20writer%20of%20%E2%80%9CTake%20Me%20Out%2C%E2%80%9D%20has%20died.%20He%20was%2067%20years%20old.%20Greenberg%E2%80%99s%20death%20was%20announced%20on%20social%20media%20by%20collaborators%20and%20colleagues%20such%20as%20Denis%20O%E2%80%99Hare%20and%20Jesse%20Tyler%20Ferguson%2C%20who%20won%20Tonys%20for%20their%20work%20in%20the%20original%202003%20production%20of%20%E2%80%9CTake%20Me%20Out%E2%80%9D%20and%20its%202022%20revival%2C