cles%2Fcm2ml8lzzrno.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Military%20experts%20weigh%20in%20on%20China's%20new%20mosquito-like%20spy%20drone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221636%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China%20showcased%20a%20new%20mosquito-sized%20spy%20drone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68654b6af748d8c055f4d08e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22802%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChina%20showcased%20a%20new%20mosquito-sized%20spy%20drone.%3Cp%3ECCTV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20month%2C%20China%20unveiled%20a%20mosquito-like%20spy%20drone%20designed%20for%20covert%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20drone's%20size%20and%20weight%20could%20limit%20its%20uses%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20military%20analysts%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20could%20still%20prove%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20new%20surveillance%20tool%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20China's%20National%20University%20of%20Defense%20Technology%20unveiled%20a%20new%20spy%20drone%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20a%20mosquito.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShowcased%20on%20the%20state-run%20CCTV-7%20military%20broadcaster%2C%20the%20micro-drone%20appeared%20to%20be%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20a%20human%20fingernail%20and%20featured%20tiny%2C%20leaf-like%20wings%20and%20thin%2C%20wiry%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20not%20look%20as%20impressive%20as%20some%20of%20the%20bigger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-defense-tech-industry-warfare-russia-attacks-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunmanned%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20coming%20out%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20its%20stick-thin%20body%20is%20said%20to%20be%20equipped%20for%20a%20range%20of%20covert%20surveillance%20and%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20drone%20to%20surveil%20buildings%2C%20especially%20on%20the%20inside%2C%20I%20can%20imagine%20it%20being%20quite%20useful%20for%20video%20feeds%2C%26quot%3B%20Herb%20Lin%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20scholar%20at%20Stanford's%20Center%20for%20International%20Security%20and%20Cooperation%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20small%20size%20may%20limit%20its%20uses%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20real%2C%20and%20powered%20conventionally%20(with%20a%20battery)%2C%20its%20longevity%20in%20the%20air%20will%20be%20limited%20by%20battery%20capacity%2C%26quot%3B%20Lin%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20it's%20very%20light%2C%20and%20therefore%20easily%20buffeted%20by%20winds.%20These%20factors%20suggest%20it%20isn't%20particularly%20useful%20for%20wide-area%20surveillance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20can%20be%20highly%20sensitive%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.register-drones.caa.co.uk%2Fdrone-code%2Fmaking-every-flight-safe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweather%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20particular%20strong%20winds%2C%20rain%2C%20snow%2C%20cold%20weather%2C%20and%20fog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20smaller%20an%20aerial%20drone%20is%2C%20the%20more%20susceptible%20it%20is%20to%20such%20conditions%2C%20Samuel%20Bendett%2C%20an%20advisor%20with%20the%20Center%20for%20Naval%20Analyses%20and%20drone%20expert%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20indoors%2C%20there%20can%20be%20conditions%20that%20could%20interfere%20with%20this%20drones'%20performance%2C%20such%20as%20even%20a%20slight%20breeze%2C%20an%20air%20flow%20from%20an%20AC%2C%20an%20open%20window%2C%20or%20other%20obstacles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommunications%20are%20another%20issue%20to%20consider%2C%20Bendett%20continued%2C%20as%20the%20drone's%20size%20means%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20much%20advanced%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20is%20technically%20possible%20to%20build%20a%20tiny%20UAV%20like%20the%20one%20displayed%20by%20the%20Chinese%20developers%2C%20its%20actual%20performance%20is%20likely%20to%20greatly%20vary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20say%20that%20the%20new%20drone%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20China's%20continuing%20innovation%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Horowitz%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20for%20technology%20and%20innovation%20at%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20said%20it%20showed%20%26quot%3BChinese%20researchers%20in%20particular%20want%20to%20push%20forward%20technological%20innovation%20in%20drones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20unclear%20how%20real%20the%20capability%20is%2C%20how%20soon%20China%20could%20field%20the%20tech%2C%20or%20the%20type%20of%20missions%20it%20could%20use%20them%20for%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilitary-experts-china-mosquito-like-spy-drones-uav-defense-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751801056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68654bb785e81483682d379d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilitary-experts-china-mosquito-like-spy-drones-uav-defense-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20micro-drone%20appears%20to%20be%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20a%20human%20fingernail%20and%20features%20tiny%2C%20leaf-like%20wings%20and%20thin%2C%20wiry%20legs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilitary-experts-china-mosquito-like-spy-drones-uav-defense-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Realty%20firm%20Signature%20Global%20purchases%20two%20land%20parcels%20in%20Gurugram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751800837000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frealty-firm-signature-global-purchases-two-land-parcels-in-gur