20extensive%20snow%20leopard%20survey%20to%20date%2C%20reports%20%3Cem%3EMongabay%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ladakh%20is%20home%20to%20an%20estimated%20477%20snow%20leopards.%20That%20is%20nearly%2068%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20entire%20snow%20leopard%20population%2C%20of%20around%20718.%20This%20two-year%20study%2C%20covering%2059%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20the%20trans-Himalayan%20region%2C%20marked%20a%20major%20milestone%20for%20snow%20leopard%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20walked%20more%20than%206%2C000%20kilometres%2C%20recorded%20nearly%2010%2C000%20signs%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343873%2Fwildlife-photographer-naturalist-in-ladakh-karamjeet-singh-snow-leopards-himalayan-brown-bear-endangered-species%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnow%20leopard%20presence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20installed%20956%20camera%20traps%20in%20high%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20low-density%20zones.%20These%20traps%20captured%20over%2026%2C000%20images.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20software%20called%20CaTRAT%2C%20trained%20specifically%20to%20recognise%20Himalayan%20wildlife%2C%20scientists%20identified%20individual%20snow%20leopards%20by%20the%20unique%20patterns%20on%20their%20foreheads%2C%20more%20reliable%20than%20side%20markings%2C%20which%20can%20be%20distorted%20by%20wind-ruffled%20fur.%20From%20126%20identified%20individuals%2C%20the%20team%20used%20spatial%20capture-recapture%20models%20to%20estimate%20a%20total%20population%20of%20477%20snow%20leopards%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ladakh%20