aybe%20it%E2%80%99s%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20marketing%20executive.%20But%20beyond%20the%20corner%20office%2C%20too%2C%20this%20sync%20persists.%20A%20conversation%20with%20the%20multihyphenate%20%E2%80%94%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20podcast%20host%2C%20author%2C%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20motivational%20speaker%20%E2%80%94%20reveals%20how%20digits%20have%20dictated%20much%20of%20his%20life.%20In%201996%2C%20Arjun%20was%20handed%20a%20prognosis%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cstrong%3E100%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20days%20to%20live%E2%80%99%20following%20a%20diagnosis%20of%20laryngeal%20cancer%20that%20had%20metastasised%20to%20the%20stomach.%20Then%20followed%20%3Cstrong%3E20%3C%2Fstrong%3E-odd%20surgeries%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fcancer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20race%20against%20time%20to%20beat%20the%20invasive%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20making%20inroads%20into%20his%20body%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20forte%20has%20always%20been%20numbers.%20And%20so%2C%20when%20from%20my%20list%20of%20interview%20questions%2C%20he%20tells%20me%20he%E2%80%99s%20biased%20toward%20number%20%3Cstrong%3E10%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20I%20smile.%20Case%20in%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20enjoy%20making%20people%20laugh.%20Did%20you%20find%20it%20in%20yourself%20to%20celebrate%20the%20small%20wins%20while%20you%20underwent%20treatment%3F%20Did%20you%20have%20any%20semblance%20of%20joy%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestion%2010%20unplugged%20a%20heavy%20stream%20of%20emotion.%20Because%20the%20dichotomy%2C%20you%20see%2C%20is%20where%20Arjun%20lived%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20his%20treatment.%20For%20someone%20who%20was%20the%20life%20of%20the%20party%2C%20effortlessly%20witty%2C%20wore%20his%20humour%20on%20his%20sleeve%2C%20and%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sustain%20a%20conversation%20without%20cracking%20a%20joke%2C%20being%20told%20he%20was%20dying%20must%20