an%20average%20student%2C%20it%20was%20sports%20and%20nature%20that%20drew%20him%20in.%20Dehradun%E2%80%99s%20proximity%20to%20the%20mountains%20ignited%20a%20passion%20that%20never%20left%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20escape%20into%20forests%20and%20mountains%20whenever%20I%20could%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vijay%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20he%20graduated%20in%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20from%20Dev%20Bhoomi%20Uttarakhand%20University%20and%20began%20working%20with%20HCL%20in%20Hyderabad.%20However%2C%20adjusting%20to%20life%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20proved%20tough.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20manage%20food%20and%20the%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20nature%20became%20his%20solace%2C%20and%20weekends%20offered%20him%20the%20perfect%20escape%20into%20the%20wilderness.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20interested%20in%20wildlife%20photography%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20I%20used%20to%20explore%20nearby%20forests.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vijay%20found%20solace%20in%20trekking%20and%20nature%20wherever%20he%20went.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T1628