t%20would%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361918%2Fadventure-map-of-india-hot-air-balloon-trekking-skiing-caving-safari-rappelling-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarting%20an%20adventure%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20impulsive%20decision.%20It%20was%20something%20Vijay%20had%20already%20mapped%20out%20%E2%80%94%20a%20well-calculated%20risk%2C%20backed%20by%20experience%20and%20a%20deep-rooted%20passion%20for%20the%20mountains.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20I%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20I%20had%20already%20planned%20what%20the%20company%20would%20be%20and%20how%20it%20would%20function%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20his%20IT%20friends%2C%20Vijay%20created%20a%20website%20and%20social%20media%20handles%20for%20AdvenThrill%2C%20so%20that%20the%20first%20wheel%20%E2%80%94%20trek%20booking%20%E2%80%94%20could%20start%20chugging.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20hired%20a%20few%20management%20interns%20to%20ensure%20the%20smooth%20running%20of%20the%20company.%20But%20I%20was%20handling%2080%25%20of%20the%20work%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162953.471-1744801205.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vijay%20had%20a%20concrete%20plan%20before%20establishing%20his%20adventure%20company.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162953.471-1744801205.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162953.471-1744801205-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-im